Package: genePackRat
Type: Package
Title: Standardized Gene Packets for QTL Follow-up Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Brian", "Gural", email = "bgural@unc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Todd", "Kimball", role = "aut"),
    person("Anh", "Luu", role = "aut"),
    person("Christoph D.", "Rau", role = "aut"))
Description: Creates standardized "gene packets" for QTL/GWAS loci containing
    multi-sheet Excel workbooks, locus zoom visualizations, and summary reports.
    Each packet consolidates gene annotations, human disease associations (Open Targets),
    mouse phenotypes (MGI), expression data, and optional founder variants. Designed
    for systematic evaluation of candidate genes in broad genomic intervals.
